OL,3,CFire that destroyed emergency phone on
OL,4,Cbeach caused by disposable BBQ
OL,6,FA fire that destroyed an emergency
OL,7,Fphone line at a Cornish beach is
OL,8,Fbelieved to have been caused by a BBQ
OL,9,Fin a bin.
OL,11,FThe blaze destroyed the bin, various
OL,12,Fsigns and a phone used by members of
OL,13,Fthe public and RNLI lifeguards during
OL,14,Femergencies on Perranuthoe Beach,
OL,15,Fknown locally as Perran Sands, near
OL,16,FPenzance.
OL,18,FResidents and visitors are being
OL,19,Fwarned to make sure BBQs are fully
OL,20,Fcooled before they are thrown away.
