OL,6,FDisposable BBQs take several hours to
OL,7,Fcool down and should not be moved or
OL,8,Fput in a bin until they are fully
OL,9,Fextinguished, using water or sand.
OL,11,FCornwall Fire and Rescue Service have
OL,12,Freleased some guidance to help the
OL,13,Fpublic when enjoying a BBQ in the sun.
